mindmap
  root((AI Initiative Roadmap))
    Phases
      Phase 0: Business Case
        Leadership defines metrics
        Strategic sign-off
      Phase 1: Cross-Functional Alignment
        Feasibility assessment
        Data evaluation
      Phase 2: Research
        R&D validation
        Tentative dates set after
      Phase 3-5: Build to Production
        Development and deployment
        Iteration loops back
    Swimlanes
      Leadership
        Metrics ownership
        Strategic decisions
      Data Science & Data
        Model development
        Data curation
      Product & Engineering
        Technical scope
        User-facing features
      Business & Ops
        Change management
        Adoption metrics
      Users
        Internal champions
        External early adopters
    Non-Negotiables
      Metrics
        Agreed upfront
        Measured throughout
      Test Data
        Curated before development
        Defines success criteria
      Change Management
        Parallel to technical work
        Training plans owned
    Key Principles
      R&D Uncertainty
        Dates tentative until validated
        Built into the plan
      Cross-Functional
        All stakeholders from start
        No siloed execution
      Iterative
        Phase 5 loops to Phase 1
        Continuous improvement